(19, 'Footer top and social networks', 'footer-top', '<div id="footer-top">\r\n<div class="wrapper clearer"><img id="vzMono" alt="VaporFi Monogram" src="/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi_theme/images/vf_monogram.png" height="113" width="186" />\r\n<div id="footer-top-text">VaporFi is an online hub coupled with brick and mortar locations serving the ever-growing and passionate vaping community. Everyone from vaping newbies to the most experienced vapers get access to the most technologically advanced electronic cigarettes and personal vaporizers. Our premium quality 100% USA-made e-liquids are offered in a large variety of flavors and are customizable for our customers'' enjoyment.</div>\r\n<ul id="footer-social-icons" class="clearer">\r\n<li><a href="http://www.twitter.com/VaporFi" target="_blank"><img alt="Twitter" src="/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi_theme/images/icon_twitter_59x59.png" height="59" width="59" /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.facebook.com/VaporFi" target="_blank"><img alt="Facebook" src="/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi_theme/images/icon_facebook_59x59.png" height="59" width="59" /></a></li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/TheVaporZone" target="_blank"><img alt="YouTube" src="/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi_theme/images/icon_youtube_59x59.png" height="59" width="59" /></a></li>\r\n<li class="last"><a href="http://www.instagram.com/vaporfi" target="_blank"><img alt="Instagram" src="/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi_theme/images/icon_instagram_59x59.png" height="59" width="59" /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-11-19 12:23:58', '2015-11-19 13:12:05', 1),
(20, 'Footer siteInfo (dafault display none)', 'footer-siteinfo', '<div id="siteInfo" class="site-info-toggle">\r\n<h1>Shop for E-Liquids<br /> VaporFi - Best Place for Custom E-Cigarette Juice</h1>\r\n<h3>Customizable E-Cigarettes and E-Liquid</h3>\r\n<p>Part of the International Vapor Group, VaporFi is the industry&rsquo;s premier manufacturer and retailer of cutting-edge <a title="buy e-cigarettes" href="#">electronic cigarettes</a>, <a title="buy e-cig accessories" href="#">e-cig accessories</a> and <a title="shop e-liquid" href="#">nicotine e-liquid</a>. Visitors to our brick-and-mortar locations enjoy a vast selection of customizable e-liquid flavors &ndash; over 30,000 flavor combinations in fact! Online patrons also enjoy the ability to mix their own e-liquid blends, and take advantage of all that e-cigarettes have to offer.</p>\r\n<h3>Find the Perfect Blend with VaporFi E-Juices</h3>\r\n<p>Have you tried what seems like dozens of e-juice combinations but have yet to find the right flavor? VaporFi e-juice bars allow you to run wild with over <a title="30,000+ e-liquid combinations" href="#">30,000+ e-liquid combinations</a> available. Many entry-level e-cigs do not allow you to customize the flavor and taste of the <a title="nicotine e-juice" href="#">nicotine e-juice</a>. While there are options in the form of pre-filled cartridges, blending your own <a title="e-juice" href="#">e-juice</a> takes vaping to a whole other level.</p>\r\n<h3>Vapor Cigarette Franchising Opportunities</h3>\r\n<p>Are you a passionate e-smoker who would like to take advantage of opportunities in this emerging electronic cigarette industry? Do you live in an area where <a title="Vapor Cigarettes" href="#">vapor cigarettes</a> would be popular, but are not easily available? Consider a <a title="vapor e-cig franchise" href="#">vapor store franchise</a> with VaporFi. Bring custom e-liquid blending and cutting-edge vapor cigarette devices to your community today. Not only are VaporFi <a 