(12, 'Review sites', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'our-company/review-sites', 'Review sites', '<div id="mainNews">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 360px;">\r\n<h1>see what the<br /> experts are <br /> saying about us</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Review Sites" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_review_sites.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h3>The following are some of the recent independent reviews of VaporFi</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Smokeless Butt Insiders</h2>\r\n<p>VaporFi is an all-American electronic cigarettes brand. The brand offers highly innovative sleekly designed electronic cigarettes, the purest e-liquid (made exclusively in the US) and plenty of other accessories to go along with their e-cig starter kits.<br /> They carry an unprecedented combination of choices that is unmatched in the industry. First off, they have your basic starter kit with standard sized e-cigs. Next they have an incredible selection of modded e cigs and tanks. On top of that, they have a massive selection of e-juice, and you can even have your own custom blend made!</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.ecigsandcoupons.com/reviews/vaporfi" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/sbi.jpg" height="24" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Vaporizer reviews</h2>\r\n<p>High-Powered Machine &ndash; Perfect For Sub Ohm Cloud Chasing, The VaporFi&trade; Vox 50 has been released, and has been very well received. If you&rsquo;re looking to get into sub-ohm vaping and create big vapor clouds, this is your baby. Not all such mods are as reliable as a VaporFi device, however. Customers rely on this company to supply only the best products and provide a 6-month warranty to prove it.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.vaporizerviews.com/box-mods/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/vaporizerviews-com_logo.png" height="25" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>best Electroniccigarette</h2>\r\n<p>Having reviewed their products, we can confidently say no other brand can compete with the performance, quality and customer care that VaporFi offers, one of the newest and most e-cig innovative brands in the market today. Overnight VaporFi has become America&rsquo;s fastest growing e-cig brand attracting both beginner and expert vapers alike.<br /> VaporFi has been making waves since its launch. Definitely worth the praise and attention, VaporFi sets itself apart from other brands due to its incredible features and designs.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://bestelectronic-cigarette.org/vapor-zone-review/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/best_ec.jpg" height="28" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>vaping360</h2>\r\n<p>We have been really impressed with Vaporfi and their brilliant products. They continue to bring out one great product after the other. We love the fact they have such a broad range of e-cigarettes, perfect for beginners and more serious vapers alike. Combine this with some seriously high quality US made eliquids and outstanding customer service and warranty, and you get one of the best vaping companies in the world. We look forward to trying more Vaporfi products in the future!</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://vaping360.com/vaporfi-coupon/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/vaping360.jpg" height="35" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>best clearomizer</h2>\r\n<p>With great power, comes great responsibility&hellip;The Vox 50 is a variable voltage/variable wattage device that knocks your watts off. The device allows you to control the power you give your device, ensuring for a powerful throat hit (or enormous clouds). The OLED digital screen makes it easy to control and monitor the power volume. The OLED screen will also give you a low voltage and high voltage warning, and the device serves to give you protection against resistance below 0.2 ohms. You can use the Vox 50 with resistances as low 0.2 ohms and all the way as high as 3.0 ohms. The Vapor quality and the vapor flavors&rsquo; max output current of the Vox 50 is 22 amps. You won&rsquo;t find a better vaping experience if you choose to buy this baby!</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.bestclearomizer.com/vaporfi-vox-50-mod-review/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/bestclearo.jpg" height="38" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>ECig Guide</h2>\r\n<p>From all of the products we got from VaporFI, we decided to save the best for last, and trust me it&rsquo;s going to be worth the wait. The VOX II MOD Starter Kit is a great &lsquo;toy&rsquo; for vaping enthusiasts and it packs one of the most powerful combos on the market today that can be fully customizable depending on the cloud chaser&rsquo;s personal preference. And by fully customizable I mean that you can choose the type of tank that comes with advanced personal vaporizer and you have three options &ndash; the Rebel, the Bolt RDA, and the Volt Hybrid Tank.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.ecigguide.com/review/vaporfi-vox-ii-mod-starter-kit" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/gallery/7/ECGLOGO.PNG" height="64" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>QuitDay</h2>\r\n<p>The top brand of 2015, VaporFi rises to the number one spot through its wide range of powerful starter kits, suitable for both beginners and advanced vapers. VaporFi is also highly regarded for quality and transparency in their popular e-liquid offerings.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="https://quitday.org/electronic-cigarettes/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/gallery/6/QuitDay_Review_Logo.png" height="38" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Best E-Cig Brands</h2>\r\n<p>The initial thought of VaporFi is the professionalism of the company. This is demonstrated, not only by their well thought out website, but also their products. They sell everything from the E-cigarette starter kits, to the e-liquids and even a number of accessories to choose from. As you dig deeper it is obvious that VaporFi doesn&rsquo;t like to cut corners when it comes to manufacturing: their thoughts are on quality.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.e-cig-brands.com/reviews/vaporfi-review/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/gallery/7/best_ecig_brands_review.jpg" height="70" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Best E Liquid Info</h2>\r\n<p>When you want to enjoy a good E-Cig you need a darn good e liquid! Let&rsquo;s face it, the e-cig itself is great but the real taste and flavor comes from the e liquid itself.<br /> At this site our goal is to bring you what we believe is the best e liquid on the planet.<br /> You&rsquo;ll find 2 things below. A chart with our favorite picks on it and why. Below that will be more information on the difference between VG and PG and our main preference.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://besteliquidinfo.com/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/best_el_info.jpg" height="60" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Smoketastic</h2>\r\n<p>VaporFi is an American electronic cigarettes brand. In the last few years, this brand has built a strong reputation among e-smokers across the world. VaporFi offers a very innovative and sleek design across all of its electronic cigarettes. Moreover, the company uses the purest form of e-liquid, specifically designed in the United States</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.smoketastic.com/reviews/vaporfi/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/smoketasticlogo.png" height="41" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>e cigarette reviewed</h2>\r\n<p>If you''re in need of more power from your e-cig, go with the VaporFi Pulse starter kit. It comes with two 750mAh batteries and two reliable clearomizers that are so easy to fill, a caveman could do it.<br /> Their e-liquid can compare with some of the premium brands as it is smooth and flavorful and available at a slightly lower cost per mL than many others.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://ecigarettereviewed.com/vapor-zone-review " target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/e-cigarette-reviewed-logo.png" height="54" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>info-Electronic-Cigarette</h2>\r\n<p>E liquid works best enjoyed when you find a flavor you enjoy and a nicotine level that satisfies your cravings. There are thousands of different flavors available however, buying the best e liquid flavor is easy when you narrow down the selection to only the highest quality vendors.<br /> Nicotine liquid, also known as e juice or e liquid, can be flavored to suit any taste or mood. Vapers enjoy the unlimited flavor combinations and the different nicotine levels that can be suited to any taste or mood. The strength varies from 0mg nicotine up to 54mg. Heavy smokers might enjoy a higher number while light smokers or people who are weening off the nicotine may enjoy the lower strengths.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://info-electronic-cigarette.com/e-liquids" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/info_electronic.jpg" height="55" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>Vaping Cheap</h2>\r\n<p>The Vaporfi Volt has a number of custom features including; signature lime-green O-rings, larger juice holes on the RBA, and a different insulator material that seems to eliminate the leaking issue associated with the Subtank Mini. The kit from VaporFi also comes with a 30ml bottle of e-juice, which adds to the total value. Meanwhile, the U.S. firm of Vaporfi offers both a 30-day money back guarantee and a 90-day warranty, making the Volt one of the best sub ohm tanks on the market today.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://vapingcheap.com/best-sub-ohm-tanks/ " target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/gallery/7/Vaporfi-jpeg.jpg" height="55" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>klks.com</h2>\r\n<p>To start our VaporFi review, it&rsquo;s important to point out who&rsquo;s behind these products. This may be a new company on the scene, but the forces behind are some of the most impressive on the e-cig landscape.<br /> International Vapor Group, who produced two of the top-rated brands on earth, Eversmoke and South Beach Smoke, created this product line. In genius fashion, they saw a clear need in the exploding electronic cigarette market for advanced personal vaporizers for people who want to take their electronic smoking to the next level in the world of eGo-style batteries, mods and tank systems.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://www.klks.com/vaporfi-review" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/klks.jpg" height="32" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>quitsmokingcommunity.com</h2>\r\n<p>Vapor Fi offers the broadest range of e-liquids on the market. They have a bunch of great premade e-liquids, and also offer you the ability to create your own blend by mixing up to 3 different flavors. But the most important thing is that their juices taste great.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="https://quitsmokingcommunity.org/e-liquid/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/quitsmoking.jpg" height="30" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>ecigone.com</h2>\r\n<p>The VaporFi Rebel II is about as close as you&rsquo;ll find to a perfect e-cigarette or vaporizer. Although we certainly can&rsquo;t claim to have tried every e-cigarette tank system on the market, the Rebel tank is the best we&rsquo;ve used by a wide margin.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://ecigone.com/e-cigarette-reviews/vaporfi-rebel-ii-review/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/eCigOne.jpg" height="44" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="newsArticle clearer">\r\n<div class="newsArticleText">\r\n<h2>spinfuel.com</h2>\r\n<p>The VOX 50 is the first 50w pocket mod from VaporFi and as a first device of this kind they gave it every feature you&rsquo;d want for performance and safety, and they made a solid, durable mod.</p>\r\n<a class="news" href="http://spinfuel.com/vaporfi-vox-50-mod-review/" target="_blank">See Review</a></div>\r\n<div class="newsArticleImg"><img alt="" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/spinfuel.jpg" height="64" width="150" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 14:50:26', '2015-12-03 14:50:26', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(13, 'Careers', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'careers', 'Careers', '<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 310px;">\r\n<h1>Careers</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Our Company" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_our_company.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h2>Join the VaporFi Team</h2>\r\n<p>Want to join a dynamic group of forward thinking of leaders? One where big ideas are put into action in a fast-paced, creative environment? Our hiring process is highly selective, but any team member will tell you that it&rsquo;s more than worth it!</p>\r\n<p>At VaporFi, we are all about our people; they are what makes us! This is an environment where your character and enthusiasm account for a great deal, and we are all about developing talent. Every one of us is passionate about what we do, and we take immense pride in working within an amazing atmosphere. We are driven to succeed, yet remain casual in the day-to-day. Everyone here knows what they bring to the table; and we are looking for like-minded, results-driven, out of the box thinking individuals who are ready to invest in their careers and futures. Apply now if you are ready to be a part of the VaporFi team; think you have what we need?</p>\r\n<h2>Commitment to Talent</h2>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;re growing rapidly, so if you&rsquo;re on the lookout for a position you do not see listed, apply anyway. Our talent acquisition department reviews all applications and resumes that are submitted, and should you be regarded as a top candidate, we hold your resume with top priority in our database. If we feel you are a fit, our talent managers will contact you to continue the process. And you can be sure that your personal information is considered confidential at all times.</p>\r\n<h2>Can You Make the Cut?</h2>\r\n<p>We are extremely selective in our hiring, and for good reason! We are forward thinking individuals who have built our organization on this same concept of new ideas. We want professionals who are down with pushing limits. VaporFi is committed to working with only the most qualified and talented, as we view the hiring process as the enhancement of our team. Apply now if you are up for the challenge!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 14:53:05', '2015-12-03 14:53:05', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Testimonials', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'our-company/testimonials', 'Testimonials', '<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 340px;">\r\n<h1>Testimonials</h1>\r\n<p>We love our customers and they love us back.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Testimonials" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_testimonials.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<p>The electronic cigarette vaporizer testimonials you&rsquo;ll find here serve the purpose of giving you perspective on how others are enjoying our products. We hope they help when making the decision if you&rsquo;re contemplating whether these products are right for you and your style of vaping. For more info on our company, starter kits, and accessories, have a look at our FAQ or contact customer service to chat directly with our friendly, experienced representatives!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>I cannot speak highly enough about these awesome products from VaporFi. I had wanted to get into better e-cigarette models for a while, and in doing my research I learned about this company. It&rsquo;s great to see this kind of performance; my enjoyment of vaping has increased 10-fold! Huge thanks to these guys!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Maggie Z. - Des Moines, IA</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 1" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_1.jpg" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>I&rsquo;ve been around the block with e-cigs, and I will tell you they are not all the same by any means. What I have found using VaporFi is that the level of power and the vapor production beat anything else I&rsquo;ve used. The batteries last forever, the quality of the USA-made e-liquids are phenomenal, and I can only say that these custom-blend flavors have really impressed me.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Stephanie S. - Ft. Lauderdale, FL</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 2" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_2.jpg" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>I am a vapor connoisseur, and these are top of the line. I am not only pleased with the selection of excellent battery models, but how powerful they all are. 2 thumbs up for the great flavors- not many brands out there give the option of blending them yourself, and this takes things to another level!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>David L. - New York, NY</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 3" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_7.png" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>Smoking cigarettes is entirely a thing of the past, and now so are the normal types of e-cigarettes. It is so much more fun and pleasurable to vape with vaporizers like these. THERE IS SO MUCH VAPOR! No annoying cartridges- which never seemed to have enough liquid in them, and no more second-rate batteries that have trouble creating more than a small puff of vapor. I still can&rsquo;t believe how advanced these are, plus for the prices the savings are incredible.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Tim S. - Green Bay, WI</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 4" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_4.jpg" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>Having been an e-smoker for some time, I can say VaporFi is the best there is. Truly amazing innovation right here, it&rsquo;s become even more enjoyable than simply smoking cigarettes ever was. Flavors, performance, and the feeling are all totally on point.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Martin S. - Riverside, CA</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 5" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_5.jpg" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="boxContentLeft">\r\n<p>Definitely the best vaporizers I&rsquo;ve ever used. Way more intense than the beginners e-cigs, and so much more to love. They do take some more effort to use, but it&rsquo;s so worth it. I would never go back to cartridges after experiencing the freedom of filling it myself. Plus the level of flavor choices rocks. Amazing quality, love the versatility of my different batteries, and really love kicking back and vaping more than ever now.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Frank H. - Miami, FL</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentRight"><img alt="Testimonial 6" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_testimonials_3.jpg" height="142" width="250" /></div>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 14:54:39', '2015-12-03 14:54:39', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(15, 'Franchising', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'our-company/franchising', 'Franchising', '<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 290px;">\r\n<h1 style="padding-top: 65px;">Franchise Opportunities</h1>\r\n<p>Join our team with your own VaporFi franchise</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Franchise Opportunities" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_store_locator.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h2>Turn-Key Vapor Franchise Opportunities in the Booming E-Cigarette Industry</h2>\r\n<p><strong><em>Bring the most unique vapor smoking devices and e-liquid, all backed by the exceptional and dedicated management team of International Vapor Group, to your area today</em></strong></p>\r\n<img class="imageFloatRight" alt="VaporFi Store Franchising" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/vz_franchising.jpg" height="450" width="350" />\r\n<p>With sales expected to exceed $2 billion in 2014 and continue growing exponentially, opportunities abound in the exciting e-cig industry, with franchising being one of the biggest.</p>\r\n<p>If you''re searching for a way to get your foot in the door in this fast-growing industry, why not consider a vapor shop franchise with VaporFi and the <a href="http://www.internationalvaporgroup.com">International Vapor Group</a>? Not only does our company manufacture the most durable VaporFi e-cigarette devices on the market, our management team has a combined 100+ years'' experience in manufacturing and distribution.</p>\r\n<p>At the helm of IVG, CEO <a href="http://www.internationalvaporgroup.com/about-us/our-team.html">Nick Molina</a> has a diverse range of experiences spanning decades, with one of his more notable accomplishments being the creation and expansion of "Let''s Talk Cellular" into a 289 store chain.</p>\r\n<p><em>Combine VaporFi''s strong management with unique VaporFi e-smoking products and e-liquid blending and you''ve got the recipe for a successful e-cigarette liquid franchise.</em></p>\r\n<p>Competition in the electronic cigarette industry is fierce, and will continue to intensify as we go from a niche product into the mainstream. If you''re an entrepreneur looking for business opportunities in this growing industry, an e-cigarette franchise through VaporFi and IVG offers several advantages, including:.</p>\r\n<h2>Why Own a VaporFi Store Franchise?</h2>\r\n<ul class="vzlist2">\r\n<li class="singleLine"><strong>We''re one</strong> of the few e-cig companies that manufacture our own products. We stand by our work 100%.</li>\r\n<li class="singleLine" style="background-color: #009ad6;"><strong>All nicotine e-liquid</strong> sold by VaporFi is manufactured in the USA</li>\r\n<li class="singleLine"><strong>Glycerin for our e-liquid</strong> comes from the Soybean, while all other ingredients are USP Grade Kosher.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;"><strong>Our custom e-liquid blending</strong> is quite unique, and gives the user literally tens of thousands of flavor combinations to choose from.</li>\r\n<li><strong>VaporFi e-cigarettes</strong> represent a smarter alternative to traditional smoking. Take pride in knowing you''re helping others improve the quality of their lives.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>VaporFi is the Only Choice For You</h2>\r\n<ul class="vzlist2">\r\n<li><strong>Since we control</strong> the production of our e-cigarettes and e-liquid, we''re able to offer a low overhead business model, which means more savings and profits for you.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;"><strong>Customers are always</strong> coming back for more. Our durable e-cig devices and exclusive e-liquid flavor blending options will keep customers returning to try new flavors or pick up their regulars.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enjoy access</strong> to an industry-exclusive revenue sharing program for Internet sales, which pays you a commission for any online sales from your area.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;"><strong>VaporFi and IVG</strong> have existing relationships with many leading shopping centers and shopping mall developers, which will be extremely helpful in finding the right location.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Choose the store format</strong> (i.e. free-standing building, shopping center inline store, mall kiosk or mall inline) that best fits with your requirements. VaporFi and IVG offer impressive flexibility, and support, in this important decision.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;"><strong>You''re never alone</strong> &ndash; near &lsquo;round-the-clock support from our exceptional management team, along with on-site training at our corporate headquarters and flagship store in Miami, Florida, are just a couple of examples of how we''re with you each step of the way.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Enjoy access</strong> to our state-of-the-art, custom Point of Sale (POS) system that gives you all of the tools you need to manage your business efficiently.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Complete Training &amp; Support</h2>\r\n<p>Our on-site training, as well as ongoing training and support, will make you an expert at both custom e-liquid blending and operating your store in no time. And if you really want to jump in with both feet, we also offer Area Developer Franchises, which allow you to develop your own network of VaporFi stores in your territory.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>The best part is you don''t need to be an e-cig aficionado to take advantage of our vapor franchising opportunities with VaporFi and IVG</strong></em></p>\r\n<small class="small-note">Learn more about e-cigarettes, e-liquid and vapor smoking in general by browsing our online store, visiting our <a href="http://blog.vaporfi.com/">blog</a> and <a href="http://www.learn.vaporfi.com/">knowledge center</a>, or visiting one of our <a href="http://www.stores.vaporfi.com/">VaporFi stores</a> in central and south Florida.</small></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 14:55:54', '2015-12-03 14:55:54', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(16, 'How It Works', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works', 'How It Works', '<div id="mainHow">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 330px;">\r\n<h1>How E-Cigs Work</h1>\r\n<p>Revolutionary. Dynamic. High-Tech.<br /> Not smoking has a new look.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="How Vaporizer Work" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_how_it_works_1.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h2>What are vaporizers, e-cigarettes, and e-liquid?</h2>\r\n<img class="imageFloatRight" alt="Vaporizers and eLiquid" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/vaporizer-cig-eliquid.png" height="377" width="246" />\r\n<p><a href="/electronic-cigarettes/">Vaporizers</a> are marvels of modern technology that millions of people around the world have chosen as an alternative for their life instead of cigarettes. Vaporizers and e-cigarettes combine form and function to allow former smokers to continue to enjoy or even eliminate their nicotine intake without the horrible smell, clothes staining ash, bad breath, and general public distaste for cigarettes.</p>\r\n<p>Vaporizers are made up of 3 main components; a battery, a tank, and an atomizer.</p>\r\n<ul class="vzlist1">\r\n<li>The <a href="/accessories/batteries/">battery </a>powers the atomizer</li>\r\n<li>The <a href="/accessories/tanks/">tank </a>holds the e-liquid</li>\r\n<li>The <a href="/accessories/atomizers/">atomizer </a>heats up the e-liquid to the point of vaporization</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">E-liquid</a>, e-juice, or vape juice is the flavored liquid put in to the vaporizer&rsquo;s tank that gets heated and inhaled. E-liquid comes in a wide variety of flavors to match every taste, from a traditional tobacco to sweet desserts to custom blended flavors. The e-liquid is also what can contain nicotine, and most vape juice is available with a range of nicotine levels to allow people switching from smoking to maintain, reduce, or eliminate their usual nicotine intake.</p>\r\n<a class="greenButton" style="width: 220px; margin: 0 auto;" href="/electronic-cigarettes/">Shop Vaporizers</a></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="mainWorks">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText">\r\n<h1 class="secundaryBannerText">Serious facts you need to know about our e-liquids</h1>\r\n<div class="bannerBtn">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h2>What is in e-liquid?</h2>\r\n<p><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">E-liquid</a> is made up of 2 main ingredients aside from any nicotine; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Propylene_glycol" target="_blank">Propylene Glycol</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glycerol" target="_blank">Vegetable Glycerin.</a> Propylene Glycol is an organic compound commonly used in such products like ice cream and soda. Vegetable Glycerin is a sugar alcohol compound commonly found as a sweetener in liqueurs and cake frosting. While these chemicals are harmless in and of themselves, it is important that you select your e-liquid from companies that you can trust as there is a wide variety of quality control in the vape juice industry which is currently unregulated.</p>\r\n<p>We take quality and safety extremely seriously which is why VaporFi e-liquids are 100% made in the USA in FDA* registered labs using better than food grade ingredients. For more information as to what sets our e-juice apart from the rest of the industry please check out our <a href="/how-it-works/why-e-liquid-rocks.html">Why Our E-liquid Rocks page.</a></p>\r\n<a class="greenButton" style="width: 220px; margin: 0 auto;" href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">Shop E-Liquids</a> <small class="small-note">* VaporFi products are not approved by the Food and Drug Administration ("FDA") nor does the FDA endorse or deem these products to be safe for use by consumers.</small></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div id="contentQuestions" class="boxContentMain">\r\n<div class="questionsText">\r\n<h2>Still have questions?</h2>\r\n<p>Vaporizers and e-cigarettes have provided a simple and fun way for millions of people to have a choice as to how they receive their nicotine. Making the switch is easier than you think, and we hope we have answered some of your questions about this amazing new technology. If you still have questions or concerns regarding vaporizers and e-liquids feel free to contact us any time, we&rsquo;re here to help. We&rsquo;re available by phone (<strong>1-855-93-VAPOR</strong>), email (<strong><a class="email-to-link" href="mailto:service@VaporFi.com">service@VaporFi.com</a></strong>), <a href="#" target="_blank">Facebook</a>, and <a href="#" target="_blank">Twitter.</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="homeMainOffers" class="boxContent1">\r\n<div id="mainBannerContainer">\r\n<div class="mainBanner">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText">\r\n<h2>Over 30,000 Flavors</h2>\r\n<div class="bannerBtn"><a class="greenButton btn-shadow" style="width: 190px;" href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">Shop E-Liquids</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Shop E-Liquids" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_mobile_banner_sample_3_pack.png" height="465" width="485" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText">\r\n<h2>From Starters to MODs</h2>\r\n<div class="bannerBtn"><a class="greenButton btn-shadow" style="width: 220px;" href="/electronic-cigarettes/">Shop Vaporizers</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Shop Vaporizers" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_mobile_banner_vaporizers-1.png" height="465" width="485" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:00:17', '2015-12-03 15:02:18', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(17, 'Tips for success', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works/tips-for-success', 'Tips for success', '<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 385px;">\r\n<h1>Tips for Success</h1>\r\n<p>Just when you thought things couldn&rsquo;t get any better.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Tips for Success" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_tips_for_success.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h2>VaporFi Tips &amp; Tricks</h2>\r\n<ul class="vzlist2">\r\n<li>Read your manual thoroughly. Seriously, when you get your starter kit, you need to take the time to get to know your products on a first-name basis.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;">If you want further info, perhaps a demo, check out the <a href="/how-it-works/videos.html">VaporFi Instructional Videos</a>. They are great for any visual referencing you need!</li>\r\n<li>Experiment! Vaporizers offer the advantage of variety, if you don&rsquo;t try out our different flavors and nicotine levels, you are missing out. The possibilities are vast. We cannot stress this enough, VaporFi offers so many different options and choices when it comes to cutting edge technology and full flavor.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;">Take flavor experimentation to the next level, play around with different drag styles. It seems crazy in thought, but different flavors just taste better with different puffing techniques! Rich flavors taste better with a long, savoring draw, while fruity and sweet flavors taste better with a swift yet deep draw.</li>\r\n<li>Prime your cartomizers by taking a couple of quick long drags. Want the best performance, vapor production and the longest lifetime possible? Prime it!</li>\r\n<li class="singleLine" style="background-color: #009ad6;">If it seems like your battery is not producing the amount of vapor you think it should be, it may need to be charged.</li>\r\n<li>Remember to charge your batteries before they get really low, or sink to the depths of 0%. This will help maintain your batteries&rsquo; lifespan overall, and can contribute to better performance in general.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;">When puffing on your e-cig, take long, slow puffs; between 1-3 seconds, not the short, quick, gaspy puffs you were accustomed to with traditional cigarettes. Find the right balance though; puffs that are too quick are not adequate, and dragging for too long can overheat the e-liquid.</li>\r\n<li>Accessories are your friends, make sure you have a good assortment of them to make the most of your vaping as well as your time.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;">Don&rsquo;t mix your products. Safety first, yo. Putting it simply, if your battery/charger/ cartomizer is not specifically made to work with other products, don&rsquo;t go playing around. We encourage you to freely use your products and get creative in certain circumstances, but not following directions can lead to trouble. And no one wants that when vaping.</li>\r\n<li class="singleLine">Dust is lame; it&rsquo;s problematic to proper functioning, so try to keep your battery or cartomizer clear of it.</li>\r\n<li style="background-color: #009ad6;">If you encounter an unwanted, unpleasant, or adverse reaction to our products, we suggest lowering your nicotine level, or choosing NO nicotine. Sadly, if that does not help, we suggest discontinuing use of these products, and heading in for a visit to your physician.</li>\r\n<li>Come check out one of our locations!;Coming in to our shop gets you one-on-one with our full array of products, flavors and our experienced electronic cigarette pros can provide real time tricks and tips.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:07:03', '2015-12-03 15:07:03', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(18, 'Learn', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works/learn', 'Learn', '<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 290px;">\r\n<h1>VaporFi Learning Center</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Learning Center" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_store_locator.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain">\r\n<h1>E-Liquid and Smokeless Electronic Cigarette How-To Guide</h1>\r\n<h4>Dive into VaporFi''s extensive knowledge resources to better understand e-smoking, smokeless cigarette devices and the literally thousands of customizable e-liquid flavors available</h4>\r\n<p>VaporFi smokeless cigarettes are different from the look-a-likes you''re used to seeing. For one, they look more like an actual &ldquo;vaping&rdquo; device rather than a cigarette look-a-like. They''re also much more durable and allow for extensive customization both in the device and the nicotine infused e-liquid.</p>\r\n<p>You''ve experimented with various e-cigarette brands out there, but have come to realize that not all electronic cigarettes are created equal.</p>\r\n<p>VaporFi devices like the Express, Pro and Air provide a much richer experience, allowing you to experiment with different e-liquid combinations among other things.</p>\r\n<p>We invite you to browse our knowledge and how-to resources below to learn more about customized nicotine e-liquid and premium electronic cigarette devices. If you''ve been a user of the less durable cigarette look-a-likes, you''ll soon learn that more exciting options await you at VaporFi.</p>\r\n<p>Bookmark us and check back often as we''re always adding new content &ndash; in the meantime, if there''s a particular topic you''d like us to explore, or you have any questions, please feel free to <a title="Contact VaporFi" href="/customer-support/">contact us</a> anytime or <a title="VaporFi Stores in Florida" href="#">visit us in-person</a> at one of our stores in central and southern Florida.</p>\r\n<small class="small-note">* VaporFi products are not approved by the Food and Drug Administration ("FDA") nor does the FDA endorse or deem these products to be safe for use by consumers.</small>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:11:08', '2015-12-03 15:11:08', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
