(19, 'Why e liquid rocks', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works/why-e-liquid-rocks', 'Why e liquid rocks', '<div id="mainWorks">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText">\r\n<h1>Serious facts you need to know about our e-liquids</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<p>e-liquids create the vapor that ends up in your body, so it is important you know where yours comes from. Vaporfi e-liquids are 100% USA made in FDA* registered labs because we want you to know exactly what you&rsquo;re getting.<br /> See below for more info.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain"><a class="blueButton" style="width: 240px; margin: 0 auto;" href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">Shop Our E-Liquids</a>\r\n<ul id="eliquid-fact-list" class="vflist">\r\n<li id="fda-registered-lab"><strong>FDA Registered Lab*</strong> - We''ve got a state of the art manufacturing facility. Our lab is registered with the FDA as a tobacco manufacturer*. <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/02_FDA_Registered_Lab.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the certification</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="top-rated-nicotine"><strong>Top-Rated Nicotine</strong> - Not all nicotine is created equal. While many look to source the most readily available an inexpensive nicotine, we only use the purest available levorotatory nicotine or l-nicotine. This is the most physiologically active type of nicotine. <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/02_Top_Rated_Nicotine.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the Nicotine report</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="top-rated-glycerin"><strong>Top-Rated Glycerin</strong> - Glycerin can be produced from any number of agents, but ours is sourced strictly from Soybean and only the highest quality producers, so most peanut allergies are not an issue. <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/03_Top_Rated_Glycerin.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the Glycerin report</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="better-than-food-grade"><strong>Better than Food-Grade</strong> - Our E-Liquid flavorings are specifically made to be inhaled, they are a step beyond &ldquo;food grade,&rdquo; and they have been GRAS approved. <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/04_Better_than_Food_Grade.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the Lab report</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="kosher-grade"><strong>Kosher Grade</strong> - Our E-Liquid base consists of USP Grade Kosher ingredients. <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/05_Kosher_Grade.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the certification</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="formulas-registered-lab"><strong>Formulas FDA Registered*</strong> - All of our formulas are on file with the FDA*; we want them to know what we&rsquo;re up to! <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/02_FDA_Registered_Lab.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the certification</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="lot-numbers"><strong>Lot Numbers</strong> - All of our products contain these handy little labels known as &ldquo;Lot Numbers&rdquo; so that all of our products can be traced to their origins.</li>\r\n<li id="child-proof-bottles"><strong>Child-Proof Bottles</strong>&nbsp;- All of our e-liquids are safely packaged in child-proof bottles (NOTE: please keep from reach of children). <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/08_Child_Proof_Bottles.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the Lab report</a>.</li>\r\n<li id="high-operation-standards"><strong>High Operation Standards</strong> - We strictly adhere to cGMP operation standards, in line with the 21 CFR part 111 guidelines.</li>\r\n<li id="diacetyl-free"><strong>Diacetyl-Free</strong> - VaporFi E-Liquids are all diacetyl-free; no fake-butter flavor here! <a class="popup-pdf" href="http://www.vaporfi.com/media/manuals/vz/10_Diacetyl_Free.pdf" target="_blank">Click to see the Lab report</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class="blueButton" style="width: 240px; margin: 0 auto;" href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">Shop Our E-Liquids</a> <small class="small-note">* VaporFi products are not approved by the Food and Drug Administration ("FDA") nor does the FDA endorse or deem these products to be safe for use by consumers.</small></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2>vapetender&reg; - flavors made fresh to order</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain"><img class="imageFloatRight" alt="E-Liquid Flavorings" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_flavorings.jpg" height="200" width="280" />\r\n<p>VaporFi''s VAPETENDER&reg; will perform their magic live as they create your special eLiquid blend using our incredible selection of flavors to fill your e-cigs with. Our eLiquids are designed to be enjoyed individually or custom blended. Our VAPETENDER&reg; will blend any combination of flavors you can dream up, giving you the option to create thousands of customized flavors to suit your individual taste preferences. We cover all types of flavors, with a well-rounded selection of different types of tobacco, a variety of menthols, and a wide selection of sweet and other flavors. We&rsquo;re aiming to please!</p>\r\n<div class="clear">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1 hide-Mobile">\r\n<div class="boxContentMain imgCustomBlend"><img class="imageFloatRight" alt="Custom Blends" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_flavors_custom_blend.png" height="278" width="428" />\r\n<h2>VaporFi E-Liquid Flavors</h2>\r\n<ul class="vzlist1">\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/tobacco-flavors/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Tobacco Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/menthol-flavors/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Menthol Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/dessert-flavors/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Dessert Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/fruit-flavors/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Fruit Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/other-flavors/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Other Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - All Flavors</a></li>\r\n<li><a href="/e-liquid-cartridges/custom-blends/custom-blend.html">VaporFi Premium E-Liquid - Custom Blending</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="popUpPdf" class="popup_block"><a class="popUpClose" href="javascript: void(0)">Close</a>\r\n<div class="popup-content">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:12:25', '2015-12-03 15:12:25', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(21, 'Refer a friend', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'refer-a-friend', 'Refer a friend', '<div id="mainReferAFriend">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 290px;">\r\n<h1>Refer A Friend</h1>\r\n<p>Give $10 &amp; You''ll Get $20</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Refer-A-Friend" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_refer_a_friend.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2>Get Paid To Tell A Friend</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<p>Give your friends $10.00 OFF their first purchase with VaporFi and when they buy it we''ll give you $20 off your next order (200 VF rewards points).</p>\r\n<ul id="rules-list">\r\n<li id="rule-1">Share us on Facebook, Twitter &amp; Email</li>\r\n<li id="rule-2">Your friends will get $10 off</li>\r\n<li id="rule-3">You will get $20 in reward points</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class="greenButton shareBtn" href="#">Share It Now</a></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2>They''re Going To Love You For It</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<p>Come on&hellip; let&rsquo;s be serious for a minute&hellip; who doesn&rsquo;t love a pal who hooks them up with sweet deals and awesome products that improve their lives for the better? If VaporFi rocks your world, chances are, our products will do the same for your friends and they''ll get 10 off their first order.</p>\r\n<a class="greenButton shareBtn" href="#">Share It Now</a></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2>It Only Takes 1 Click to Earn $20</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<p>Referring your friends takes a few seconds using our 1 click system. You can share with your friends on Facebook, Twitter or by email and we''ll take care of the rest to track your referral fees. Everyone''s a winner, you''ll get $20 for every new friend that places.</p>\r\n<a class="greenButton shareBtn" href="#">Share It Now</a></div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:18:20', '2015-12-03 15:18:20', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(23, 'VaporFi Rewards Points', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works/rewards', 'VaporFi Rewards Points', '<div id="mainRewards">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="margin: 0 40px 0 340px;">\r\n<h1 style="font-size: 44px; line-height: 62px; padding-top: 35px;">VaporFi Rewards Points</h1>\r\n<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Shop n Share To Earn Free Products</h2>\r\n<p>Use your VaporFi points to order free vaporizers, E-liquids or accessories. Best of all they are completely free. Check all the fun ways below to earn your fee points.</p>\r\n<p>For every <strong>1 dollar</strong> spent with us, you will earn <strong>1 point</strong>. When you earn <strong>200 points</strong>, you will get a <strong>$20 credit towards VaporFi products!</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Loyalty Program" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_rewards.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2><span>1</span> Earn Free Points For Shopping, Reviews &amp; More</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<ul class="circle">\r\n<ul class="circle">\r\n<li>Rewards Points can be used on any future orders, even Sales items.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<small>* Make sure you create an account and are logged in when shopping to be eligible for points.</small>\r\n<ul class="bullet-points">\r\n<li id="rewards-dollar">\r\n<h4>1 VF Point</h4>\r\n<p>Every $1 Spent</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li id="rewards-hdp" class="tall">\r\n<h4>25 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>Sign up for Home Delivery Program</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li id="rewards-reviews" class="tall">\r\n<h4>1 VF Point</h4>\r\n<p>Leaving a product review</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li id="rewards-bday">\r\n<h4>20 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>It''s your Birthday</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2><span>2</span> Get Free Points When Your Friends Order</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<p>Through the VaporFi Rewards Club you can send your friends an exclusive $10 OFF their first order. After their first purchase, we will give you $20 in Rewards Points as a thank you.</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-points">\r\n<li id="rewards-buys" class="wide">\r\n<h4>200 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>Referred friend buys</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="box-head">\r\n<h2><span>3</span> Earn Free Points For Shopping, Reviews &amp; More</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box-info">\r\n<p>Share it with your friends on Facebook and get points for sharing. You can share as many products as you want (limited to 3 shares per day).</p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-points">\r\n<li id="rewards-fblike" class="tall">\r\n<h4>5 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>Share VaporFi on Facebook</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li id="rewards-twitter" class="tall">\r\n<h4>5 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>Share VaporFi on Twitter</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li id="rewards-share" class="tall">\r\n<h4>5 VF Points</h4>\r\n<p>Share your entire purchase</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:22:54', '2015-12-03 15:22:54', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(24, 'Instructional videos', 'one_column', NULL, NULL, 'how-it-works/videos', 'Instructional videos', '<div id="mainVideos">\r\n<div class="boxContent1">\r\n<div class="boxBannerFull">\r\n<div class="boxBannerBottom">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class="mainBanner2">\r\n<div class="mainBannerText" style="width: 390px;">\r\n<h1>Instructional Videos</h1>\r\n<p>Lights. Camera. Action.&nbsp; Easy-to-follow instructional videos make getting started easy.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="mainBannerImg"><img alt="Instructional Videos" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/main_secondary_banner_videos.png" height="316" width="980" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxContentMain"><img class="imageFloatRight" alt="Instructional Videos" src="http://www.vaporfi.com/skin/frontend/default/vaporfi/images/img_video.jpg" height="196" width="220" />\r\n<p>Need some vaping coaching? Want to have an in-depth view of our products before you purchase? Have a look at our instructional videos, designed to help guide you if you&rsquo;re in need of a visual demonstration.</p>\r\n<p>Sometimes you need more than reading a manual full of instructions; and that&rsquo;s exactly why we&rsquo;ve produced these videos. Not to brag or anything, but we think our videos are pretty awesome, too. We hope our videos offer some insight, some direction, and help you figure things out when you need it. And of course, if you have a recommendation for a new instructional video, please let us know and we''ll create one.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="boxBottom1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2015-12-03 15:24:32', '2015-12-13 22:47:07', 1, 0, '<reference name="content">\r\n    <block type="cms/block"  name="banners_4_in_bottom">\r\n        <action method="setBlockId"> \r\n            <block_id>banners-4-in-bottom</block_id> \r\n        </action> \r\n    </block>\r\n</reference>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
